Hmm, I can't really work out what exactly is going wrong there. I 
suspect that the fact that ppc64 uses kmem_cache_alloc() for 
__pud_alloc() -> pud_alloc_one() whereas x86 uses the page allocator is 
the culprit here.
Eduard, thoughts?
